\s1 E navir averiabar aven guiz…®n gumazamizibagh ifongegh
\p 
\v 9 Eght…® ia ifar gumazibagh ifongan mark…®, ia uan navir averiabar aven guiz…®n gumazamizibagh ifongegh. Egh arazir kurabar aghuagh…®va, egh arazir aghuibar suiragh gavgafigh.
\v 10 Ia uan ik…®zim…®n aven uari uarigh ifongez…® mogh…®n, ia uaghan Krais…®n adarazir aven uari uarigh ifongegh. Egh zurara ia uarira uan ziaba p…®raf…®s…® pamtem ingar.
\v 11 Ia pamten ingar…®va am…®rvaghan mark…®, eght…® God…®n Duam ian navibar amut…® ia zurara Ekiam…®n ingangarim damus…® naviba d…®kavam.
\v 12 Egh ia, bizir aghuir ia fogha iniamiba bagha m…®zua, dagh n…®ghn…®gh bar akongegh. Egh os…®mt…®ziba izamin dughiam…®n, ia ik…® uaghan da ater…®va tugh gavgafigh. Egh zurara God ko m…®k…®m.
\p 
\v 13 Eght…® God…®n gumazamiziba biziba puvat…®ght…®, bizir ia itiba men akurvagh. Eght…® nguibar igharazim…®n gumaziba ian bighan izamin dughiam…®n, ia me inigh uan d…®penibar mang…® deragh me damu.
\v 14 Gumazim arazir kuram…®n n…® damight…®, n…® arazir aghuim…®n a damus…® God…®n azangs…®gh. Egh a gas…®ghas…®ghs…® God…®n azangs…®ghan mark…®.
\v 15 Eght…® igharaz darazi bar akongeght…® ia me ko bar akongegh. Egh igharaz darazi osemeght…®, ia me ko osemegh.
\v 16 Egh ia arazir vabara, gumaziba bar me damu. Egh uarira uari fan mark…®. Egh gumazir ziaba puvat…®zibar namakabar amu. Kamagh…®n uab…® g…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, k…®rara fofozim iti.
\p 
\v 17 Gumazitam arazir kuratam…®n n…® damight…®ma, n…® uam arazir kuram…®n a ikarvaghan mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia zurara gumazibar damazim…®n derazir arazibar amu.
\p 
\v 18 Ia uari navir am…®rizim ik…®va gumazir igharaziba ko navir vam…®ra ik…®s…® pamtem ingar.
\v 19 Nan namakar aghuiba, me arazir kuram ia damight…®, eght…® ia men arazir kuram ikarvaghan mark…®. Ia teght…®, God uab…® uan an…®ngagharim…®n tuavim…®n me ikarvagham. Ia fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven en Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiarvazim nan ingangarim, k…® uab…® men arazir kuraba ikarvagham.‚Äù
\v 20 Egh n…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n damu, ‚ÄúN…®n apanim, m…®tiriam an agh…®t…®, n…® daghem a dan…®ng. Eght…® kuarim an p…®rt…®, n…® d…®patam a dan…®ng. N…®n arazir aghuir kam a damight…®, a uan arazir kuram g…®n…®ghn…®gh bar aghums…®gham.‚Äù
\v 21 N…® arazir kuram ateght…®, a n…® gafighan mark…®. N…® arazir aghuim damut…®, n…®n arazir kam arazir kuram ab…®ragh a gafiragham.
\c 13
\s1 E gavman…®n apengan ikiam
\p 
\v 1 Gumaziba bar gavmanbar apengan ik…®. E fo, gavman tam puram otozir puvat…®. Gavman…®n ingangariba God…®n dafarimram oto. Gavman…®n aven itir gumazir dapaniba bar, God uab…® me ar…®ki.
\v 2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, gumazitam gavman…®n dapanibar akam batogha, kamagh…®n a God uab…® ingangarir kam damuasa m…®sevezir gumazibar akaba batosi. Gumazir kamagh…®n amiba, me uari uan arazibar ivezir kuraba iniam.
\v 3 Gavmanba gumazir arazir aghuibagh amiba atiatim me dan…®ngasa itir puvat…®. Gavmanba gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba atiatim me dan…®ngasa iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® gavman…®n atiatingan koghs…®, n…® arazir aghuibar amut…®, eght…® me n…®n ziam fam.
\v 4 E fo, gavman a God…®n ingangarir gumazim, egha an arazir aghuibar, ian akurvaghasa ia bagha ingari. N…® arazir kuram damigh gavman…®n atiating. N…® fo, gumazibagh as…®gh…®s…®ghamin ingangarim ko gavgavim gavman…®n dafarim…®n iti, a puram aning…®n suirazir puvat…®. A God…®n ingangarir gumazim, n…® tina arazir kuram damight…®, a n…®n arazir kuram…®n ivezim n…® dan…®ngam.
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® gavmanbar apengan ik…®. Ia gavman apengan ikian kogh, ivezir kuram iniam, kar guizbang…®ra. Ez…® ia uaghan kamagh…®n fogh, ia uan navir averiam…®n aven uan araziba derav…®ra da tuis…®gh, arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damuva, egh ia gavmanbar apengan ikiam.
\p 
\v 6 Gavmanba God…®n ingangarir gumazibar ik…®, zurara ingangarir God me gan…®ngizim deragh a damu. Bizir kam bagh ia uaghan takis…®n dag…®aba is…® me dan…®ngam.
\v 7 Bizir tizir ia gavmanba dan…®ngamiba, ia me dan…®ng. Takis…®n dag…®aba ko takis…®n igharazir maba sara, me dan…®ng…®va, egh arazir aghuibar me damu, egh men ziaba f…®.
\s1 E gumazamizir igharaziba bar me gifuegham
\p 
\v 8 Ia ikarvaghamin biziba, tam ikian mark…®, ia bar da g…®fagh. Eght…® ikarvaghamin bizir mam zurara ikiam. A kamak…®n: e gumazir igharaziba bar me gifuegham. Tina gumazir igharaziba bar me gifonge, a guizbang…®ra Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n zui.
\v 9 E fo, Moses Osirizir Araziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazibav soght…®, me ar…®m…®gh…®ran mark…®. Ia ok…®man mark…®. Ia gumazir igharazibar biziba bagh naviba d…®kavan mark…®. Ia poroghamiba uari bak…®m uari ko dakuan mark…®.‚Äù Moses Osirizir Arazir kaba ko maba sara uaghan iti, da bar mogh…®ra akar vam…®ra an aven iti, akar kam kamak…®n: ‚ÄúN…® uab…®ra uab…® gifongezir mogh…®n, gumazir igharazibagh ifongegh.‚Äù
\v 10 N…® gumazir igharazim gifongegh, arazir kuratam…®n a damighan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazim igharaz darazigh ifongegha, a Moses Osirizir Araziba guiz…®n dar g…®n zui.
\s1 E angazangarim…®n aruir gumazibar m…®n daruam.
\p 
\v 11 Dughiar e dat…®r…®gh…®n itim, ia a g…®fo, kamagh…®n arazir k…® ia m…®kemeziba ia dar amu. Kar dughiar ia daguraguim ategh d…®kavigh angamra ikiamim. Ia fo, fom…®ra dughiar e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n itim, koma God en akuraghamin dughiam…®n, aning mong uaning…®n saghon iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n God en akurvaghamin dughiar kam a rogh…®ra ize.
\v 12 Am…®n…®rb…®rim g…®vasava amima, am…®nim tiasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e m…®tatem…®n araziba bar dar ategh…®va angazangarim…®n aven m…®soghs…® m…®dorozir biziba inigh dar aghuigh.
\v 13 E angazangarim…®n aruir gumazibar m…®n deraghv…®ra daruam. E d…®par onganibar am…®va onganan kogh, egh pura gumazamiziba is…® pamten d…®m…®va ighiar kurabar arazibar amuan mark…®. Egh gumaziba ko amiziba pura tintinibar uari ko dakuva, afiar arazibar amuan mark…®. Egh uari uariv sogh…®va, egh munav…®n biziba bagh navim ikuvigh…®va da inis…® navim isian mark…®.
\v 14 Egh ia uan Ekiam Krais Iesus arugh, mati gumazim m…®dorozir biziba aghui. Ia uan navir ghurim…®n arazibagh n…®ghn…®gh…®va, egh navir ghurim…®n ifongiam uam an g…®n mangan mark…®.
\c 14
\s1 Ia uan adarazir araziba tuis…®ghan mark…®, egh suam, ian araziba ikufi
\p 
\v 1 Gumazim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ikia, egha an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gavgavizir puvat…®, ia gumazir kam inigh aven iz…®t…® a ian tong…®n ikiam. Ia, an navir averiam…®n aven itir n…®ghn…®ziba bagh, a ko uari adoghan mark…®.
\v 2 Gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itim, a biziba bar a dapi. Ez…® gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim mong gavgavizir puvat…®zim, an as…®ziba apir puvat…®.\f + \ft (14:2) Ia akar 1 Korin 8:1…®n itim…®n gan.\f*
\v 3 Gumazir biziba bar da apim, gumazir as…®ziba apir puvat…®zim girak…®rang…®n adarir n…®ghn…®zibar gumazir kam damuan mark…®. Eght…® uaghan gumazir as…®ziba apir puvat…®zim, a fo, God a iniz…® a sios…®n aven ize, kamagh…®n, a gumazir biziba bar da apim…®n arazibar gan da tuis…®ghan mark…® egh suam, an araziba ikufi.
\v 4 N…® tina, n…® ghaze, k…® ti gumazir igharazim…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n araziba tuis…®gham. Puvat…®. Bizir a tugh gavgavigham o a ir…®ghamim, kar an Gumazir Ekiam…®n bizim. Ekiam uab…® a damight…® a gavgavigham, kamagh…®n a guizbang…®ra tugh gavgavigham.
\p 
\v 5 Gumazitam suam, dughiar mam dughiar mabagh afira. Eght…® gumazir igharazim suam, dughiaba bar magh gari. Eght…® gumaziba bar vaghvagh uari g…®fogh suam, n…®ghn…®zir manam men n…®ghn…®zim…®n dera.
\v 6 Gumazir dughiar mam p…®rafim, an Ekiam…®n ziam fasa kamagh…®n ami. Ez…® gumazir biziba bar a da apim, a dagheba bagha God m…®nabi, egha tuavir kam…®n Ekiam…®n ziam fe. Gumazir as…®ziba apir puvat…®zim, a God m…®naba, Ekiam…®n ziam fasa n…®ghn…®gha, egha dagher maba ataghrasi.
\p 
\v 7 E fo, en tong…®n itir gumazitam suam, nan ik…®r…®m…®rir angamra itim, a nan bizimra puvat…®. Eght…® gumazitam suam, nan ovevem, uaghan nan bizimra puvat…®.
\v 8 E angamra ik…®va, e Ekiam bagh ikiam. E aremegh, e Ekiam bagh aremegham. Kamagh…®n, e angamra iti, o areme, e Ekiam…®n adarazira.
\v 9 Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n. Krais aremegha ua d…®kafi. Kamagh…®n an angamra itiba ko aremeziba bar mogh…®ra men Ekiam…®n iti.
\p 
\v 10 E fo, e bar God…®n kotiam…®n tuivight…®, an en araziba tuis…®gham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® uab…®, n…® uan adarazir araziba tuis…®ghan kogh suam, men araziba ikufi. N…® uab…®, n…® uan adarazir g…®rak…®rang…®n adarir n…®ghn…®zibar me damuan mark…®.
\v 11 E fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® ian Ekiam, k…® zurara ik…®v…®ra ikiam, kamagh…®n k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei,
\q2 ‚ÄòNguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar nan guam…®n uan teviba ap…®r,
\q3 egh uan akabar nan gun m…®k…®m suam, k…® guizbang…®ra God.‚Äô‚Äù
\b
\m 
\v 12 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e bar vaghvagh uan arazir amizibar gun God…®n m…®k…®mam.
\s1 N…® uan tav damut…®, an arazir kuram damuan kogham
\p 
\v 13 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e gumazir igharazibar araziba ua da tuis…®ghan kogham. Egha ia n…®ghn…®zir igharazim…®n g…®n mang…®va, egh e uan adarazir amut…® me arazir kuram damuva iran kogham.
\v 14 K…® Ekiam Iesus ko poroghav ikia, ez…® bizir kam nan n…®ghn…®zim gamiz…® a bar kuiaghr…®z…®, k…® guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n fo, bizitam uab…® God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir puvat…®. Eght…® gumazitam suam, bizir manam an damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®, eght…® bizir kam an n…®ghn…®zim…®n guizbang…®ra bar m…®ze, eght…® an a damuan mark…®.
\v 15 Kamagh…®n, n…® daghetam ram…®t…®, n…®n anav gan n…®ghn…®gh suam, a God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze, eght…® arazir kam…®n n…® an n…®ghn…®zim gas…®ghas…®gham. N…® kamagh…®n damuva n…® munav gifongezir arazim…®n g…®n mangan kogham. Krais munav bagha areme, ez…® n…® puram apir arazim a damuva a gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®.
\v 16 Egh ia kamagh…®n damuan mark…®, ia igharaz darazir amut…®, me ian arazir aghuim m…®k…®m suam, ia arazir kuram gami.
\v 17 E fo, gumazitam, God Bizibagh Ativir Arazim m…®k…®ms…®, a dagheba apir araziba o d…®paba apir araziba dav k…®man kogham. Puvat…®. A God…®n damazim…®n derazir arazim ko, navir vam…®ran ikiamin arazim ko, bar akongezir arazim, dav k…®mam. Arazir aghuir kaba, da God…®n Duam…®n aven otifi.
\v 18 Eght…® tina tuavir kam…®n Krais…®n ingangarim damigh, a God damut…®, an a bagh bar akuegham. Eght…® a gumazamizibar amut…®, me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuibar a m…®k…®mam.
\p 
\v 19 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e zurara igharaz darasi ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin arazibar g…®n mang…®va, egh arazir gumazir igharazibar amut…® me tugh gavgavighamiba, dar g…®n mang…® dar amuam.
\v 20 N…® daghemra n…®ghn…®gh, tuavir kam…®n God amizir arazibagh as…®ghas…®ghan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, dagheba bar, da dera. Eght…® n…® daghetam ram…®t…®, bizir kam gumazir igharazim damight…®, an arazir kuram damigh ir…®gham, eght…® kamagh…®n n…® arazir kuram gami.
\v 21 Kar tuavir aghuim, n…® kamagh…®n damuan mark…®: n…® as…®zitam ko wain…®n d…®patam ram…®va egh bizir igharazitam damight…®, da n…®n anav damight…® a ir…®gham.
\v 22 N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir bizir kam…®n itim, a n…®n navim…®n ik…®. God n…®n n…®ghn…®zim g…®fo, eght…® n…® gumazir igharazitam…®n m…®k…®man mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, gumazitam bizitam g…®n…®ghn…®zima, bizir kam dera, ez…® an navim osemezir puvat…®, gumazir kam bar akongegham.\f + \ft (14:22) Grigh…®n akam vez…®n kam…®n deragha bigha m…®kemezir puvat…®.\f*
\v 23 Gumazitam asizitam o daghetam am…®va, egh n…®ghn…®zir pumuning ik…®t…® God a m…®k…®m suam, an arazir kuram gami. An amir arazir kam, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gis…®n tuzir puvat…®, kamagh…®n os…®mt…®zim an iti. Guizbang…®ra, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gis…®n tughan kogh arazir manam damut…®, God suam, an arazir kuram.
\c 15
\s1 E Krais…®n n…®ghn…®zim ko arazim…®n g…®n mangam
\p 
\v 1 E gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itiba, gumazamizir gavgaviba puvat…®ziba, men os…®mt…®ziba ater men akurvagham. E uarira uarir akurvaghs…® n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.
\v 2 E bar vaghvagh uan adarazi bagh pamten ingar men akurvagham. E kamagh sua, men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gavgavigh ik…®v…®ra ikiam, kamagh…®n e men akurvagham.
\v 3 E fo, Krais uab…® uab…®n akurvaghasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n arazir a batozim…®n osizirim kamak…®n, ‚ÄúAkar kurar gumaziba n…® gaseziba, da uaghan na gire.‚Äù
\v 4 God…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar me fom…®ra God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n osiriziba, da bar en sure damuasa me ada osiri. M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam e damut…®, e n…®m…®ra ik…®, os…®mt…®ziba ater…®va tugh gavgavigh God e dan…®ngamin bizir aghuiba bagh m…®zuamam.
\v 5 Dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® ia bagha God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, God uab…® e gamima, e n…®m…®ra ikia os…®mt…®ziba atera tugha gavgafi. Egh a ia damut…®, ia Krais Iesus amizir arazibar g…®n mang…®, egh tuavir kam…®n ia igharaz darazi ko navir vam…®ra ikiam.
\v 6 Kamagh…®n k…® ia bagh God…®n azangs…®ght…®, ia navir vam…®ra ik…®va bar mogh…®ra uari inigh God…®n ziam fam, an en Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n Afeziam.
\s1 Krais, Judaba ko Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba uaghan, bar men akura
\p 
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba God…®n ziam f…®s…®, ia Krais…®n adarasi ia uarira uari inigh bar akongegh. Krais ia inigha aven izez…® mogh…®n, ia igharaz darazi inigh aven iz…® bar akongegh.
\v 8 K…® ia m…®gei, Krais Judabar ingangarir gumazim…®n oto. A n…®ghn…®zir kam faraghav…®ram an iti, a kamagh…®n men akagham, God m…®kemezir akaba da bar guizbang…®ra. Da kamak…®n, God en ovaviba ko amizir akar d…®k…®r…®ziba, da guizbang…®ra otivigham.
\v 9 Krais uaghan kamagh sua, a Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazibar amight…®, me God…®n apangkuvim bagha an ziam fam. God…®n Ak…®nafarim bizir kam kamagh…®n a m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazibar tong…®n ik…®va n…® m…®nabam.
\q2 Egh k…® n…®n ziam f…®va ighiabar amuam.‚Äù
