\v 10 Egha God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®g…®r…®g…®ar igharazim uaghan iti,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúIa Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba, ia God…®n gumazamiziba Israelba,
\q2 ia me ko ik…® bar akongegh.‚Äù
\b
